    <p><img alt={"moviedb"} src={require("!url-loader?limit=10000&name=assets/images/[name]-[hash].[ext]&fallback=file-loader!./f.png").default} />{`
`}<img alt={"moviedb"} src={require("!url-loader?limit=10000&name=assets/images/[name]-[hash].[ext]&fallback=file-loader!./g.png").default} /></p>
    <p>{`To be able to rate movies a user needs to be logged in: for that a basic JWT-based authentication system is implemented, where user details are stored in the RedisGraph for persistence.`}</p>
